    Our luggage is designed by travelers, for travelers

    At Away, you’ll find suitcases, bags, and accessories built with thoughtful details to make each and every journey more seamless.

    Learn more

    The original better Carry-On luggage

    Our hard shell Carry-On suitcases are lightweight but durable, with 360° wheels that keep you moving resistance-free. Need to lift? The extra grab handles are sure to become your new best friend. You'll also find our patented inner compression system in The Carry-On, The Bigger Carry-On, and The Carry-On Flex, so you'll be primed for smart packing no matter which style you love.

    The best Carry-On suitcases let you express your personality. Our Softside Carry-Ons come in multiple colors to match your style and have zippered expansion—for when you can't decide on what to bring. The luxuriously soft exterior is also easy to clean and water-resistant for travel in any type of weather. Along with the 360° wheels and proprietary stabilizer, The Softside Carry-On suitcase has multiple pockets, plenty of grab handles, and a complimentary laundry bag for easy separation.

    Knowing how to pack a Carry-On suitcase starts with the right luggage. Luckily, we've got the bag—and accessories—for that. Our Carry-Ons come with an inner compression system to let you get more into your suitcase, and we've upgraded the compression panel with mesh pockets for more storage. One side of your suitcase can store larger pieces, while the other zipped compartment works perfectly with The Insider Packing Cubes and our other packing organizers. These organizers keep everything tidy and at hand—no more digging around!
